[Intro]
  Luuqadan Go waxa curiyey ama sameyey developers-ka ka shaqeeya shirkada Google, 
  hadafka ama yoolka luuqadan wuxu ahaa in la fudeediyo dhisida applications-ka 
  baaxada wayn iyado luuqadan laga dhigayo mid sahlan oo si fudud lo adeegsan karo. 
  Luuqadan waxaad ku dhisi karta: Web servers & APIs, Command-line tools (CLI), 
  Cloud services & DevOps tools, Networking tools, Microservices architecture, 
  Data processing pipelines.
[end]
